data.meta_description: A collection of the early Bermuda newspapers, focusing on the "Bermuda Gazette and Weekly Advertiser," "Bermuda Gazette", "Weekly Gazette and Bermuda Advertiser," and "The Royal Gazette, Bermuda Commerical and General Advertiser and Recorder".
